OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fsunny spells will gradually give way
OL,7,Fovernight to thickening cloud from the
OL,8,Fnorthwest. Perhaps some spots of rain
OL,9,Fovernight, mainly over the Peak
OL,10,FDistrict. Turning a little breezy, but
OL,11,Fmild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FSunny spells for most, but
OL,14,Fthicker cloud at first in the
OL,15,Fnorthwest. Isolated showers are
OL,16,Fpossible, especially over the Peak
OL,17,FDistrict. Breezy, and cooler than of
OL,18,Flate.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
